46:04.196 --> 46:07.590
Yeah, but what they said
didn't matter.

46:07.590 --> 46:10.158
What you said did.

46:12.291 --> 46:13.771
And then I'll see you
in a little bit,

46:13.771 --> 46:16.295
and-- and [chuckles], what?

46:16.295 --> 46:18.253
Nothing.

46:18.253 --> 46:21.256
For 12 years until I seek
you out.

46:21.256 --> 46:23.519
Via my daughter.

46:25.652 --> 46:28.394
Well, I mean,
that just happened.

46:28.394 --> 46:30.613
You just happened to
seek me out on the Internet

46:30.613 --> 46:34.139
and run into her
and somehow just end up,

46:34.139 --> 46:39.492
whoops, falling in love
with my child?

46:39.492 --> 46:43.148
She's an amazing person,

46:43.148 --> 46:45.106
but I'm sure
you already know that.

46:49.458 --> 46:52.070
Whatever you think
you have with Anna, it's over.

46:52.070 --> 46:53.332
You're going to
ruin that, too.

46:53.332 --> 46:57.292
- She's 16.
- She's 17.

46:57.292 --> 46:59.904
And that's your argument?

46:59.904 --> 47:02.863
That she's too young?
- That is different.

47:02.863 --> 47:04.169
Why?

47:04.169 --> 47:05.518
Because she's a girl?

47:05.518 --> 47:07.302
No.

47:07.302 --> 47:10.131
The difference is
and this is a huge difference,

47:10.131 --> 47:12.568
is nothing ever happened
between you and me.

47:17.095 --> 47:21.142
What do...

47:21.142 --> 47:22.491
What do you mean?

47:22.491 --> 47:23.841
- This isn't good, Jesse?
- What do you mean

47:23.841 --> 47:25.494
nothing happened?
- Something happened,

47:25.494 --> 47:27.148
just not what you think,
not what you told the school.

47:27.148 --> 47:31.457
- How can you even say that?
- Because it's the truth.

47:31.457 --> 47:33.589
I know this might be hard
for you to hear,

47:33.589 --> 47:36.941
but it's important
that you hear it.

47:36.941 --> 47:40.335
We were close, too close.
That's on me.

47:40.335 --> 47:43.338
I was the adult, and I should
have known better, but--

47:43.338 --> 47:47.212
But what?

47:47.212 --> 47:52.652
This thing happens,
happens sometimes, Jesse.

47:52.652 --> 47:56.090
People want things to be
a certain way,

47:56.090 --> 48:00.051
and so they begin to believe
that it's true.

48:06.884 --> 48:08.102
Hold on.

48:08.102 --> 48:10.148
Particularly when you're young,

48:10.148 --> 48:11.932
and there's nothing
wrong with that.

48:11.932 --> 48:14.979
You know, I think
that goes both ways, too.

48:14.979 --> 48:17.546
What do you mean?

48:17.546 --> 48:19.200
That some people don't want
to remember something

48:19.200 --> 48:21.855
so they block it out?

48:21.855 --> 48:24.684
I hear about that, too.

48:24.684 --> 48:28.383
It doesn't mean there's
something wrong with you.

48:28.383 --> 48:31.212
- Jesse.
- Beth.

48:33.475 --> 48:38.219
I had always hoped
that you found some help.

48:38.219 --> 48:43.311
And I'm sorry that no one ever
stepped in to help you.

48:45.792 --> 48:47.837
You need to go home.

48:47.837 --> 48:50.405
- I don't have a home.
- Well, I do.

48:50.405 --> 48:53.756
And I don't ever want
to see you near it again.

48:53.756 --> 48:55.280
Move away from the door.

49:06.595 --> 49:09.250
Sorry.

49:09.250 --> 49:11.383
I should probably move that, right?

49:11.383 --> 49:14.125
Please, Jesse.

49:14.125 --> 49:15.778
There you go.
It's perfect.

49:15.778 --> 49:17.911
You want to tell him everything
or should I?

49:19.739 --> 49:22.263
I mean this in the most
caring way possible.

49:22.263 --> 49:24.526
You need to speak with someone.
- Yeah.

49:24.526 --> 49:27.225
You.

49:27.225 --> 49:28.791
Everything okay?

49:28.791 --> 49:30.924
Can you please
just move your car?

49:30.924 --> 49:33.318
Yeah. Hey, Beth.

49:33.318 --> 49:36.190
When you see Anna,

49:36.190 --> 49:38.540
tell her that nothing happened, okay?

49:38.540 --> 49:40.281
That there is no love
between us.

49:40.281 --> 49:42.805
That it's just her overly active
imagination, that it's just

49:42.805 --> 49:44.633
some sort of psychotic
wish fulfillment at work.

49:44.633 --> 49:47.462
Can you tell her that for me?
Please, get some help.

49:47.462 --> 49:49.899
You want to help me?

49:49.899 --> 49:51.640
Tell the truth?
- What truth?

49:51.640 --> 49:53.294
That you were in love with me

49:53.294 --> 49:54.643
as much as I was
in love with you.

49:54.643 --> 49:58.212
I want to hear you
say it out loud.

49:58.212 --> 49:59.997
Say it!
- Okay.

50:01.824 --> 50:03.304
Let's think about this
for a second.

50:08.657 --> 50:10.485
There's two ways this could go.

50:10.485 --> 50:13.401
You want to know what they are?
- Sure.

50:13.401 --> 50:16.404
I can handcuff you,
arrest you, trespassing,

50:16.404 --> 50:18.798
maybe resisting arrest,
haul you off to jail,

50:18.798 --> 50:21.061
hand you off to my real
good buddies down there.

50:21.061 --> 50:22.454
It's not my favorite way.

50:22.454 --> 50:26.588
It's inefficient
for both you and me.

50:26.588 --> 50:29.417
You want to know the second way?

50:29.417 --> 50:31.506
I'm guessing you do,
so here it is.

50:31.506 --> 50:32.812
Get in your truck.

50:32.812 --> 50:37.034
You go home,
all the way home,

50:37.034 --> 50:38.905
and you never come back.

50:40.863 --> 50:43.083
How do I know this plays out?

50:43.083 --> 50:44.519
Because I have your plates.

50:44.519 --> 50:46.608
I have everything about you.
I know you.

50:46.608 --> 50:47.957
I got you.

50:50.351 --> 50:53.311
So yeah,
what do you think?

50:53.311 --> 50:55.052
Option two?

50:58.359 --> 51:00.057
Yep.

51:01.188 --> 51:03.625
Yeah, that's what
I would do, too.

51:03.625 --> 51:05.105
Smart.

51:07.499 --> 51:09.327
I get it.

51:13.853 --> 51:15.289
You're not
the first person to abuse

51:15.289 --> 51:16.943
their power over me.

51:19.989 --> 51:21.469
Right, Beth?

51:21.469 --> 51:23.558
Hey, Eric.

51:23.558 --> 51:26.170
What do you think?

51:26.170 --> 51:27.823
You think this is over?

51:27.823 --> 51:30.696
This whole messed up thing
that you're doing here?

51:30.696 --> 51:31.914
You think it's done?

51:34.961 --> 51:37.006
Yeah.

51:37.006 --> 51:40.271
Yeah, I do.

51:40.271 --> 51:41.576
Me, too.

52:26.099 --> 52:28.145
I was embarrassed.

52:34.020 --> 52:36.065
Okay.

52:36.065 --> 52:37.806
And?

52:41.201 --> 52:44.726
I was embarrassed,
so I didn't say anything.

52:48.600 --> 52:51.733
Well, maybe now is a pretty
good time to start talking.

52:59.828 --> 53:02.701
His name is Jesse, first off.

53:05.573 --> 53:08.750
He was a student of mine
at the academy.

53:11.492 --> 53:13.755
Okay.

53:13.755 --> 53:16.323
I never wanted to have
to tell you this.

53:16.323 --> 53:20.284
Jesus, Beth.
Spit it out.

53:20.284 --> 53:22.547
There was a scandal.

53:24.462 --> 53:26.681
Or a near scandal.

53:28.683 --> 53:30.032
I was accused of having

53:30.032 --> 53:33.122
an inappropriate relationship
with him.

53:35.386 --> 53:38.954
Yeah, a sexual relationship.

53:42.654 --> 53:47.006
I took him under my wing
too much.

53:50.575 --> 53:55.623
He developed
these feelings for me.

53:58.626 --> 54:00.280
- Okay.
- And he ended up

54:00.280 --> 54:04.284
creating this fiction.

54:06.591 --> 54:09.855
But I bear some
of the responsibility, too.

54:09.855 --> 54:13.380
He's right. It should have
never been personal.

54:13.380 --> 54:15.164
We should have never...

54:17.515 --> 54:18.907
gotten close.

54:18.907 --> 54:22.041
Hmm, okay, okay.

54:53.115 --> 54:55.814
- No prior arrests?
<i>- Nothing.</i>

54:55.814 --> 54:58.338
<i>Looks like he lives in an
apartment that his parents own.</i>

54:58.338 --> 55:01.646
<i>Not in school, I'm not even
sure he has a job.</i>

55:01.646 --> 55:03.256
Hmm. Alright.

55:03.256 --> 55:04.388
Let's keep an eye out
for those tags.

55:04.388 --> 55:06.128
Understood?
<i>Absolutely.</i>

55:12.613 --> 55:14.659
Hey.

55:14.659 --> 55:16.443
We need to talk.

55:16.443 --> 55:18.271
What is there to say?

55:20.404 --> 55:22.188
I owe you a huge apology.

55:24.364 --> 55:27.976
There's things
I haven't told you.

55:27.976 --> 55:29.804
A lot of things.

55:31.719 --> 55:37.203
So, he knew who I was
when we started talking online?

55:37.203 --> 55:41.294
I can only assume
that he was looking for me.

55:41.294 --> 55:49.476
Came across you and decided to
use you to get to me, I guess.

55:49.476 --> 55:52.392
I'm so sorry, honey.

55:56.440 --> 55:58.790
Why didn't you say anything?

56:02.359 --> 56:06.188
I saw him there and I froze.

56:06.188 --> 56:10.932
I panicked,
and it immediately brought me

56:10.932 --> 56:13.021
back to that time
when you were four years old

56:13.021 --> 56:17.504
and I let this kid
get too close to me.

56:17.504 --> 56:19.288
You should have told me.

56:25.904 --> 56:29.516
I was embarrassed
and just sick

56:29.516 --> 56:31.475
that I had brought
this heartache on you.

56:31.475 --> 56:34.129
Anna.
- Mom, just please.

57:23.744 --> 57:26.573
I assigned a patrol car
to your street,

57:26.573 --> 57:28.401
keep an eye on you and Anna.

57:28.401 --> 57:30.185
Good.

57:30.185 --> 57:31.970
How's Anna?

57:34.538 --> 57:37.279
Distant.

57:37.279 --> 57:40.979
Yeah.
She'll be all right.

57:40.979 --> 57:43.721
Yes, eventually.

57:46.158 --> 57:50.249
I do you have a bit
of other news?

57:50.249 --> 57:52.773
- What?
- The caterer said they could do

57:52.773 --> 57:54.906
the poppyseed ham biscuits
after all.

58:16.318 --> 58:17.929
Come in.

58:22.586 --> 58:25.502
Hey, want some dinner, honey?

58:25.502 --> 58:27.112
Huh?

58:46.218 --> 58:48.133
Okay, you got to get
out of your head

58:48.133 --> 58:51.789
and do something dumb and fun.

58:51.789 --> 58:55.357
Remember how you hounded me
after Jake pulled that shit

58:55.357 --> 58:57.142
that he pulled on me?

58:57.142 --> 59:00.058
I'm here to hound you back.

59:00.058 --> 59:02.974
I just don't get it.

59:02.974 --> 59:05.672
Well, there's nothing
to get, really.

59:05.672 --> 59:07.456
You just landed a psychopath.

59:07.456 --> 59:10.547
Or a psychopath landed on me,
which makes me an idiot.

59:10.547 --> 59:13.854
The last thing you are
is an idiot.

59:13.854 --> 59:15.769
Let's just focus on the fact

59:15.769 --> 59:18.076
that you just dodged
a big, fat bullet.

59:40.838 --> 59:42.491
No! No!

01:00:37.546 --> 01:00:38.809
Hey.
- Hey.

01:00:46.947 --> 01:00:48.949
You're here.

01:00:48.949 --> 01:00:50.429
So I am.

01:01:03.921 --> 01:01:06.663
Wow.
You're killing it.

01:01:06.663 --> 01:01:08.316
Thanks.

01:01:08.316 --> 01:01:09.970
- You heading out?
- Uh, yeah.

01:01:09.970 --> 01:01:12.625
I'm going to pick up Brit
a little before the party.

01:01:12.625 --> 01:01:14.366
- Okay.
- Okay.

01:01:22.896 --> 01:01:25.116
I love you, Mom.

01:01:25.116 --> 01:01:27.161
I love you too, baby.

01:01:46.224 --> 01:01:48.792
<i>They're trying to get me
to test the wine.</i>

01:01:48.792 --> 01:01:50.228
- Uh-oh.
<i>- Come on.</i>

01:01:50.228 --> 01:01:53.013
<i>The caterers
are already setting up.</i>

01:01:53.013 --> 01:01:58.976
Hey, this is your
last chance to bail.

01:01:58.976 --> 01:02:01.587
We'd only owe for the catering.

01:02:01.587 --> 01:02:03.371
<i>Not a chance.</i>

01:02:03.371 --> 01:02:05.243
Shit.
I need you to zip me up.

01:02:05.243 --> 01:02:07.332
<i> I got to go.
The florist is here.</i>

01:02:07.332 --> 01:02:08.812
<i>Love you.</i>
- You, too.

01:02:08.812 --> 01:02:12.337
Anna?

01:02:12.337 --> 01:02:13.904
Is that you?

01:02:13.904 --> 01:02:15.427
Hey, can you come sit me up?

01:02:17.342 --> 01:02:18.735
Sure.

01:02:20.301 --> 01:02:23.696
Don't call your cop fiancé.

01:02:23.696 --> 01:02:25.306
Please, just give me a second.

01:02:25.306 --> 01:02:27.178
You cannot be here.

01:02:27.178 --> 01:02:29.180
And then I'll leave.

01:02:29.180 --> 01:02:32.139
They're expecting me
any minute.

01:02:32.139 --> 01:02:34.751
Do you know why I'm here?

01:02:34.751 --> 01:02:36.753
You've put me
through enough, Jesse.

01:02:36.753 --> 01:02:40.452
So, no, I don't know
and I just can't care anymore.

01:02:43.847 --> 01:02:46.066
I think you will, though.

01:02:46.066 --> 01:02:49.635
I really do.

01:02:49.635 --> 01:02:51.942
First things first.

01:02:51.942 --> 01:02:54.335
I'm here for Anna.
- Well, you can forget that.

01:02:54.335 --> 01:02:55.859
Hmm?

01:02:55.859 --> 01:02:57.512
She's not here,

01:02:57.512 --> 01:03:00.472
and she will never go
anywhere with you.

01:03:00.472 --> 01:03:02.430
No?

01:03:02.430 --> 01:03:04.868
She knows who you are, Jesse.

01:03:04.868 --> 01:03:07.348
She knows everything.

01:03:09.437 --> 01:03:10.787
You're right about that.

01:03:15.095 --> 01:03:16.836
Maybe you should
check her room.

01:04:10.368 --> 01:04:13.850
So maybe you care
a little now.

01:04:13.850 --> 01:04:15.764
What do you want from me?

01:04:20.030 --> 01:04:22.206
No one believed me.

01:04:25.992 --> 01:04:27.776
Not even my dad.

01:04:29.648 --> 01:04:31.563
My mom, I think she wanted to,

01:04:31.563 --> 01:04:36.437
but mostly I think
she just wanted it to go away.

01:04:38.657 --> 01:04:43.053
The embarrassment to go away.

01:04:43.053 --> 01:04:47.187
For her, for the school.

01:04:47.187 --> 01:04:50.974
And then you are the only person
I ever trusted.

01:04:50.974 --> 01:04:54.194
You-- you turned on me, too.

01:04:54.194 --> 01:04:57.502
I heard what you said about me.

01:04:57.502 --> 01:05:00.461
Troubled, delusional, I think
were your words of choice.

01:05:00.461 --> 01:05:04.117
Jesse, no.

01:05:04.117 --> 01:05:05.902
And then our phone call.

01:05:07.991 --> 01:05:11.037
Do you remember?

01:05:11.037 --> 01:05:15.346
- No.
- I'll see you in a little bit.

01:05:19.350 --> 01:05:23.223
And then I never heard another
word from you again.

01:05:23.223 --> 01:05:28.489
Jesse, this is not something
that we can settle now.

01:05:28.489 --> 01:05:30.839
We--
- I tried to kill myself.

01:05:34.104 --> 01:05:37.237
Yeah.

01:05:37.237 --> 01:05:39.196
That happened.

01:05:41.198 --> 01:05:44.897
I mean I failed, obviously.

01:05:46.899 --> 01:05:49.249
Jesse.

01:05:49.249 --> 01:05:52.252
But to have you call
me a liar...

01:05:55.690 --> 01:06:00.173
We can't do this,
just the two of us.

01:06:00.173 --> 01:06:01.783
We need to talk to someone.

01:06:01.783 --> 01:06:04.525
- Mnh-mnh.
- Just give me my phone.

01:06:04.525 --> 01:06:06.440
I don't need
to talk to someone, Beth.

01:06:06.440 --> 01:06:09.661
I need to talk to you.

01:06:09.661 --> 01:06:14.971
But since I've been here, I...

01:06:14.971 --> 01:06:16.885
What, Jesse?

01:06:18.975 --> 01:06:20.889
Can I show you something?

01:06:36.166 --> 01:06:37.906
Please?

01:06:52.747 --> 01:06:54.445
Here.

01:06:56.708 --> 01:07:01.930
This was that year.
This was spring of that year.

01:07:01.930 --> 01:07:06.413
- Yes.
- I mean, your hair is--

01:07:06.413 --> 01:07:09.025
your hair is short.

01:07:09.025 --> 01:07:14.421
Yeah, I cut it
over the holidays and...

01:07:14.421 --> 01:07:16.380
kept it short.

01:07:18.469 --> 01:07:21.037
Because I cannot be more
perfectly sure

01:07:21.037 --> 01:07:24.344
that your hair
was long that spring.

01:07:24.344 --> 01:07:25.780
I could not be more sure.

01:07:25.780 --> 01:07:28.348
I mean, I-I remember
specific occasions.

01:07:28.348 --> 01:07:33.875
I remember your hair,
I remember your face.

01:07:33.875 --> 01:07:35.094
But you are--
you're in--

01:07:35.094 --> 01:07:37.662
you're in this picture, and...

01:07:40.969 --> 01:07:43.059
It was short then.

01:07:43.059 --> 01:07:45.452
I'm like feeling, like,
messed up

01:07:45.452 --> 01:07:47.367
about all of this right now.

01:07:53.939 --> 01:07:57.334
I mean, what?
Did I just want it so bad?

01:07:57.334 --> 01:07:59.858
Did I want it so bad
that I-- that I made it up.

01:07:59.858 --> 01:08:02.208
You know?
I mean, like...

01:08:02.208 --> 01:08:04.254
It happens, Jesse.
It's okay.

01:08:04.254 --> 01:08:06.647
And everything that I've done
since falling

01:08:06.647 --> 01:08:09.911
for Anne and now?
I mean, Jesus Christ.

01:08:09.911 --> 01:08:12.610
Because if that's-- if that's
the case, Beth, then--

01:08:12.610 --> 01:08:14.394
then-- then--
- Then what?.

01:08:14.394 --> 01:08:17.093
Then I'm a fucking idiot!

01:08:19.486 --> 01:08:21.314
God! Like, delusional.

01:08:21.314 --> 01:08:23.011
I'm like what
everybody says I am.

01:08:23.011 --> 01:08:24.709
I'm wrong.
I'm a liar.

01:08:24.709 --> 01:08:29.061
Like, all of these years.
Like, what-- what is that?!

01:08:30.802 --> 01:08:33.326
I ruined everything.
I ruined everything.

01:08:33.326 --> 01:08:35.111
I ruined your life.

01:08:35.111 --> 01:08:38.375
I mean, I know how much you love
teaching, and I ruined that.

01:08:38.375 --> 01:08:42.161
And I hate myself
for doing that!

01:08:42.161 --> 01:08:43.945
Oh, my God.

01:08:53.303 --> 01:08:55.696
I don't understand.

01:09:28.468 --> 01:09:30.209
It's funny.

01:09:32.298 --> 01:09:36.520
You're looking at this photo
as proof of a truth.

01:09:38.696 --> 01:09:40.698
All I see is a lie.

01:09:46.573 --> 01:09:48.662
We look happy.

01:09:51.926 --> 01:09:54.842
Gary was abusive, cheating.

01:09:59.195 --> 01:10:01.022
This photo's bullshit.

01:10:02.894 --> 01:10:05.244
I wasn't a capable mother.

01:10:08.291 --> 01:10:09.944
I just wasn't.

01:10:16.690 --> 01:10:20.216
And then that night in the car.

01:10:20.216 --> 01:10:23.915
If I had told the truth,
I would have gone to prison.

01:10:27.092 --> 01:10:30.878
They would have taken Anna
from me.

01:10:30.878 --> 01:10:32.445
You get that, right?

01:10:32.445 --> 01:10:34.142
What truth?

01:10:36.144 --> 01:10:38.059
That I had fallen in love
with you.

01:10:46.546 --> 01:10:48.722
You were in love with me?

01:10:48.722 --> 01:10:50.942
It was wrong.

01:10:50.942 --> 01:10:52.509
Mnh-mnh.

01:10:54.554 --> 01:10:57.296
Mnh-mnh.

01:10:57.296 --> 01:11:00.038
Maybe not the feelings,
but the acting on them.

01:11:02.432 --> 01:11:03.694
What do you mean?

01:11:06.740 --> 01:11:08.568
The sex, Jesse.

01:11:12.920 --> 01:11:14.705
What happened in the car.

